{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"442e881635","title":"和郭沫若题齐白石画","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"327023e322","index":0,"year":1950,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"442e881635"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"ef5bbe56c1","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"442e881635","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东和郭沫若在齐白石的一幅画上的题字。"},{"id":"e2bc87605a","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"442e881635","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"丹青，中国古代绘画常用朱红、青色，故称画为“丹青”。丹青意造本无法，化用宋代苏转《石苍舒醉墨堂》“我书意造本无法，点画信手烦推求”之句。"},{"id":"17ff0d9cf6","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"442e881635","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"圣，谓所专长之事造指至于极顶。画圣，绘画艺术大师。画圣胸中常有诗，化用宋代陆游“此老胸中常有诗”之句。"}],"contents":[{"id":"499a8eacad","type":"title","text":"和郭沐若题齐白石画”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"442e881635"},{"id":"ef5bbe56c1","type":"paragraph","text":"丹青意造本无法；（毛泽东）画圣胸中带有诗。（郭沫若）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"442e881635"}],"page":{"id":"39266ef850","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"442e881635","start":494,"end":494}}}},"__N_SSG":true}